		<div id="comment_body_64194514"><blockquote><div><p>Whenever did Christ advocate using force of government (weapons in your face) to compel people to "help" the poor by forcibly depriving the rich and middle class of their property (stealing) in order to redistribute it to the poor and the lazy?</p></div></blockquote><p>Ignoring your very leading question, <a href="https://biblemesh.com/blog/what-did-jesus-teach-about-paying-taxes/#:~:text=Since%20even%20secular%20authority%20comes,or%20the%20government%20is%20godless." title="biblemesh.com">Matthew 22:21</a> [biblemesh.com].</p></div>
